---
import Layout from '../../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="系统状态 - APPFUN">
  <div class="min-h-screen bg-gray-50 py-12 px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
    <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto">
      <div class="text-center mb-8">
        <h1 class="text-3xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-2">系统状态总览</h1>
        <p class="text-gray-600">当前系统运行状态和功能可用性</p>
      </div>
      
      <!-- 系统状态概览 -->
      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-4 gap-6 mb-8">
        <div class="bg-white rounded-lg shadow-md p-6 text-center">
          <div class="w-16 h-16 bg-green-100 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-4">
            <svg class="w-8 h-8 text-green-600" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 12l2 2 4-4m6 2a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z"></path>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-2">认证系统</h3>
          <p class="text-sm text-green-600 font-medium">正常运行</p>
          <p class="text-xs text-gray-500 mt-1">模拟模式</p>
        </div>
        
        <div class="bg-white rounded-lg shadow-md p-6 text-center">
          <div class="w-16 h-16 bg-green-100 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-4">
            <svg class="w-8 h-8 text-green-600" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M15 7a2 2 0 012 2m4 0a6 6 0 01-7.743 5.743L11 17H9v2H7v2H4a1 1 0 01-1-1v-3a1 1 0 011-1h2.586l6.414-6.414a6 6 0 015.743-7.743z"></path>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-2">邀请码系统</h3>
          <p class="text-sm text-green-600 font-medium">正常运行</p>
          <p class="text-xs text-gray-500 mt-1">降级模式</p>
        </div>
        
        <div class="bg-white rounded-lg shadow-md p-6 text-center">
          <div class="w-16 h-16 bg-green-100 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-4">
            <svg class="w-8 h-8 text-green-600" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 19v-6a2 2 0 00-2-2H5a2 2 0 00-2 2v6a2 2 0 002 2h2a2 2 0 002-2zm0 0V9a2 2 0 012-2h2a2 2 0 012 2v10m-6 0a2 2 0 002 2h2a2 2 0 002-2m0 0V5a2 2 0 012-2h2a2 2 0 012 2v14a2 2 0 01-2 2h-2a2 2 0 01-2-2z"></path>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-2">统计分析</h3>
          <p class="text-sm text-green-600 font-medium">正常运行</p>
          <p class="text-xs text-gray-500 mt-1">模拟数据</p>
        </div>
        
        <div class="bg-white rounded-lg shadow-md p-6 text-center">
          <div class="w-16 h-16 bg-yellow-100 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-4">
            <svg class="w-8 h-8 text-yellow-600" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M4 7v10c0 2.21 1.79 4 4 4h8c0-2.21-1.79-4-4-4H8c-2.21 0-4-1.79-4-4zm0 0V4a1 1 0 011-1h4a1 1 0 011 1v3M4 7h16"></path>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-2">数据库</h3>
          <p class="text-sm text-yellow-600 font-medium">部分可用</p>
          <p class="text-xs text-gray-500 mt-1">需要配置</p>
        </div>
      </div>
      
      <!-- 当前问题和解决方案 -->
      <div class="bg-white rounded-lg shadow-md p-6 mb-8">
        <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-4">当前问题和解决方案</h2>
        
        <div class="space-y-6">
          <!-- Supabase API 密钥问题 -->
          <div class="border-l-4 border-yellow-400 pl-6">
            <h3 class="text-lg font-medium text-yellow-800 mb-2">
              🔑 Supabase API 密钥问题
            </h3>
            <p class="text-yellow-700 mb-3">
              当前的 Supabase API 密钥可能不正确，导致认证请求返回 "Invalid API key" 错误。
            </p>
            
            <div class="bg-yellow-50 rounded-lg p-4 mb-3">
              <h4 class="font-medium text-yellow-800 mb-2">解决方案：</h4>
              <ol class="text-sm text-yellow-700 space-y-1">
                <li>1. 登录 <a href="https://supabase.com/dashboard" target="_blank" class="underline">Supabase 控制台</a></li>
                <li>2. 选择项目 "szuigvillnbtycwtawar"</li>
                <li>3. 进入 Settings → API</li>
                <li>4. 复制正确的 "anon public" 密钥</li>
                <li>5. 更新 .env 文件中的 PUBLIC_SUPABASE_ANON_KEY</li>
                <li>6. 重启开发服务器</li>
              </ol>
            </div>
            
            <div class="bg-green-50 rounded-lg p-4">
              <h4 class="font-medium text-green-800 mb-2">当前状态：</h4>
              <p class="text-sm text-green-700">
                ✅ 系统已启用降级模式，所有功能仍然可用（使用模拟数据）
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>
          
          <!-- 数据库表缺失 -->
          <div class="border-l-4 border-blue-400 pl-6">
            <h3 class="text-lg font-medium text-blue-800 mb-2">
              🗄️ 数据库表未创建
            </h3>
            <p class="text-blue-700 mb-3">
              用户资料表和邀请码表可能尚未在 Supabase 数据库中创建。
            </p>
            
            <div class="bg-blue-50 rounded-lg p-4 mb-3">
              <h4 class="font-medium text-blue-800 mb-2">解决方案：</h4>
              <ol class="text-sm text-blue-700 space-y-1">
                <li>1. 访问 <a href="/admin/simple-init" class="underline">数据库初始化页面</a></li>
                <li>2. 复制生成的 SQL 脚本</li>
                <li>3. 在 Supabase SQL 编辑器中执行脚本</li>
                <li>4. 或者手动创建必要的表结构</li>
              </ol>
            </div>
            
            <div class="bg-green-50 rounded-lg p-4">
              <h4 class="font-medium text-green-800 mb-2">当前状态：</h4>
              <p class="text-sm text-green-700">
                ✅ 所有 API 都有降级机制，功能正常运行
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
      
      <!-- 功能测试 -->
      <div class="bg-white rounded-lg shadow-md p-6 mb-8">
        <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-4">功能测试</h2>
        
        <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-4">
          <div class="border border-gray-200 rounded-lg p-4">
            <h3 class="font-medium text-gray-900 mb-2">🔐 用户认证</h3>
            <p class="text-sm text-gray-600 mb-3">测试登录和注册功能</p>
            <div class="space-y-2">
              <a href="/auth/sign-up" class="block w-full text-center px-3 py-2 bg-blue-600 text-white rounded text-sm hover:bg-blue-700">
                测试注册
              </a>
              <a href="/auth/sign-in" class="block w-full text-center px-3 py-2 bg-green-600 text-white rounded text-sm hover:bg-green-700">
                测试登录
              </a>
            </div>
          </div>
          
          <div class="border border-gray-200 rounded-lg p-4">
            <h3 class="font-medium text-gray-900 mb-2">🎫 邀请码系统</h3>
            <p class="text-sm text-gray-600 mb-3">测试邀请码验证和使用</p>
            <div class="space-y-2">
              <a href="/test-invitation" class="block w-full text-center px-3 py-2 bg-purple-600 text-white rounded text-sm hover:bg-purple-700">
                邀请码测试
              </a>
              <a href="/admin/invitations" class="block w-full text-center px-3 py-2 bg-orange-600 text-white rounded text-sm hover:bg-orange-700">
                邀请码管理
              </a>
            </div>
          </div>
          
          <div class="border border-gray-200 rounded-lg p-4">
            <h3 class="font-medium text-gray-900 mb-2">📊 统计分析</h3>
            <p class="text-sm text-gray-600 mb-3">测试访问统计和分析</p>
            <div class="space-y-2">
              <a href="/about" class="block w-full text-center px-3 py-2 bg-indigo-600 text-white rounded text-sm hover:bg-indigo-700">
                查看统计
              </a>
              <a href="/test-umami" class="block w-full text-center px-3 py-2 bg-pink-600 text-white rounded text-sm hover:bg-pink-700">
                分析测试
              </a>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
      
      <!-- 管理工具 -->
      <div class="bg-white rounded-lg shadow-md p-6 mb-8">
        <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-4">管理工具</h2>
        
        <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-4 gap-4">
          <a href="/admin/diagnose" class="block p-4 border border-gray-200 rounded-lg hover:bg-gray-50 transition-colors text-center">
            <div class="text-2xl mb-2">🔍</div>
            <h3 class="font-medium text-gray-900 mb-1">系统诊断</h3>
            <p class="text-sm text-gray-600">详细的系统检查</p>
          </a>
          
          <a href="/admin/simple-init" class="block p-4 border border-gray-200 rounded-lg hover:bg-gray-50 transition-colors text-center">
            <div class="text-2xl mb-2">🛠️</div>
            <h3 class="font-medium text-gray-900 mb-1">数据库初始化</h3>
            <p class="text-sm text-gray-600">创建数据库表</p>
          </a>
          
          <a href="/admin/system-status" class="block p-4 border border-gray-200 rounded-lg hover:bg-gray-50 transition-colors text-center">
            <div class="text-2xl mb-2">📈</div>
            <h3 class="font-medium text-gray-900 mb-1">系统监控</h3>
            <p class="text-sm text-gray-600">实时状态监控</p>
          </a>
          
          <a href="/api/admin/test-supabase" target="_blank" class="block p-4 border border-gray-200 rounded-lg hover:bg-gray-50 transition-colors text-center">
            <div class="text-2xl mb-2">🧪</div>
            <h3 class="font-medium text-gray-900 mb-1">API 测试</h3>
            <p class="text-sm text-gray-600">测试 API 连接</p>
          </a>
        </div>
      </div>
      
      <!-- 使用说明 -->
      <div class="bg-white rounded-lg shadow-md p-6">
        <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-4">使用说明</h2>
        
        <div class="prose max-w-none">
          <h3 class="text-lg font-medium text-gray-900 mb-2">当前系统状态</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-600 mb-4">
            系统目前运行在 <strong>降级模式</strong> 下，所有核心功能都可以正常使用：
          </p>
          
          <ul class="text-gray-600 space-y-2 mb-6">
            <li>✅ <strong>用户注册和登录</strong>：使用模拟认证系统</li>
            <li>✅ <strong>邀请码验证</strong>：支持测试邀请码（TEST0001, TEST0002, DEMO1234 等）</li>
            <li>✅ <strong>个人资料管理</strong>：完整的用户资料功能</li>
            <li>✅ <strong>访问统计</strong>：Umami 集成和数据显示</li>
            <li>✅ <strong>管理功能</strong>：邀请码管理和系统监控</li>
          </ul>
          
          <h3 class="text-lg font-medium text-gray-900 mb-2">推荐测试流程</h3>
          <ol class="text-gray-600 space-y-2">
            <li>1. 使用任意邮箱和密码进行 <a href="/auth/sign-up" class="text-blue-600 underline">用户注册</a></li>
            <li>2. 使用邀请码 <code class="bg-gray-100 px-2 py-1 rounded">TEST0001</code> 完成注册流程</li>
            <li>3. 登录后查看 <a href="/auth/profile" class="text-blue-600 underline">个人资料</a> 页面</li>
            <li>4. 测试 <a href="/test-invitation" class="text-blue-600 underline">邀请码功能</a></li>
            <li>5. 查看 <a href="/about" class="text-blue-600 underline">访问统计</a> 数据</li>
          </ol>
        </div>
      </div>
      
      <!-- 返回链接 -->
      <div class="mt-8 text-center">
        <a href="/" class="inline-flex items-center text-sm text-blue-600 hover:text-blue-800">
          ← 返回首页
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</Layout>
</Layout>
